    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含第一则故事（完整版共四则），游玩时间约10分钟。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/a55c64c9fc740a69ee106c58aa9ef8fa.poster.avif?t=1764862910\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/a55c64c9fc740a69ee106c58aa9ef8fa.webm?t=1764862910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/a55c64c9fc740a69ee106c58aa9ef8fa.mp4?t=1764862910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恐怖故事・揭露真相</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一则则恐怖故事，将越来越与三人娘切身相关。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事列表： </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 百合街的噩梦 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 死怪谈之会 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 假想朋友 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. ？ ？ ？ ？ ？ </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/dbd8839f284e96bb7627b5bf26f60a81.poster.avif?t=1764862910\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/dbd8839f284e96bb7627b5bf26f60a81.webm?t=1764862910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/dbd8839f284e96bb7627b5bf26f60a81.mp4?t=1764862910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>增添悬疑感的剪影立绘</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三人娘说故事时，剧中剧立绘将采复古的剪影，以酝酿不安的气氛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/debfa83d3a73212f130774ad791e74a8.poster.avif?t=1764862910\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/debfa83d3a73212f130774ad791e74a8.webm?t=1764862910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/debfa83d3a73212f130774ad791e74a8.mp4?t=1764862910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「鬼就在我们之中……」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人会说鬼故事，但说鬼故事的不一定是人，或许有「某种存在」已混入三人娘…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/c6daa0384a927b6950caeedefec79154.avif?t=1764862910\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>琍琍</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵研社新社员，暗恋小涵。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「那噩梦就是一种诅咒，一种您不散布它、就会成真的诅咒。」</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/68b2b94dc86a8317e61fb14a47ebddad.avif?t=1764862910\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小涵</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >普通的女大学生，是他邀琍琍加入灵研社的。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「而我要说的，正是一则『一起听鬼故事』的鬼故事。 」</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/be33058383ecd912d1a64f053977844c.avif?t=1764862910\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>碧贤</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵研社社长，发起了这次的集会。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「这故事是从我朋友那边听来的……」</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334370/extras/86ecc305ca0f8465ec5b8f7067283abd.avif?t=1764862910\" width=300 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>勒喉女</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专挑女生下手的女鬼。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>「你喜欢蓝项圈，还是红项圈？」</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直播与游戏实况之规范</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许直播与游戏实况。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许营利，但仅限于以影音网站的功能营利。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若能在直播或游戏实况的标题加入游戏名称，或在说明栏列出Steam页面的连结，我方将不胜感激。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直播与游戏实况所导致的任何损害，我方概不负责。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本规范如有变更，恕不另行通知。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >注意</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏使用わたおきば（ Wataokiba）的可商用立绘素材，并遵守其利用规约。</p>",
